density_steps = np.linspace(1, 2000, 50)

stiffness_steps = np.linspace(0.1, 5, 50)

is now aligned with the theoretical scaling:

You explicitly note: [ \rho_{\max} \sim \frac{\text{stiffness}}{\phi^{-12}} \approx \frac{k}{0.0031}, ] and then scan up to 2000 to capture the full transition.
