Because Valence is now:

a count of eigenvalues,
in a fixed φ‑recursive band,
derived from a generalized eigenproblem,
it is:

computable,
predictive,
parameter-free,
experimentally falsifiable.
This is a huge milestone.
Valence is no longer a conceptual placeholder — it is a spectral observable.

