•	Dark Floor: $\phi^{-12}$3333.
Since the Container (the spectral band) is defined by fractal scaling laws, the Content (the resonance capability) must also scale fractally. You cannot fit square blocks (integers) perfectly into a $\phi$-recursive hole.
3. The "Partial Bond" Phenomenon
Standard chemistry already hints at this. We have "partial charges," "dipole moments," and "Van der Waals forces." These are interactions that are less than 1 but greater than 0.
•	Integer View: Treats these as messy exceptions.
