🌟 6. The refined statement
Here’s the corrected, RCFT clean version:
The spectral position of eigenmodes is determined by the cooperative balance between Sp(8) inertia and SO(9) geometry.
Coherence — and therefore valence — emerges when this balance places modes inside the φ recursive U(1) band.
This is the most accurate framing.
